 the classification of noncontrolling", "bbox": [177.2, 1268.9, 1094.4, 1285.6]}, {"text": "interests. Prior year results have been recast to conform to the current year presentation.", "bbox": [177.2, 1289.8, 761.8, 1306.4]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [143.8, 1323.1, 162.3, 1339.8]}, {"text": "The Corporation’s basic and diluted earnings per share amounts for 2005 to 2008 have been recast to include certain share-based", "bbox": [177.2, 1323.1, 1094.3, 1339.8]}, {"text": "payment awards as participating securities under the two-class method, as required by accounting requirements.", "bbox": [177.2, 1343.9, 921.9, 1360.6]}, {"text": "14", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}